// ItemCard (dashboard)
// Card showing a diagram, document, or design item with its icon, type badge, and last-modified time.

FUNCTION formatRelativeTime(timestamp) -> string
  Converts a numeric timestamp to a relative string ("just now", "5m ago", etc.).

---

FUNCTION getItemIcon(type) -> ReactNode
  Returns an SVG icon appropriate for the item type (diagram cube, document page, design layout, spreadsheet grid).

---

FUNCTION ItemCard(props) -> ReactNode                                     EXPORT
  Renders a clickable card with the item's icon, name, type badge, and relative last-modified time.
  Highlights with a selection ring when isSelected is true.
  Calls onClick when clicked.
